{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"100563-anand","title":" Anand, l'éboueur au grand cœur","description":"Viens faire la connaissance d'Anand ! Il aime conduire et rencontrer de nouvelles personnes. Il aime la musique, la danse et les animaux. Il aime être beau et il aime que les rues soient belles. Bref, il est génial ! ","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sak Untala"],"illustrators":["Rajiv Eipe"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/100563-anand"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/524491/size3/5a749282e0877bdf46bf87ebe6d7102f.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/524491/size6/5a749282e0877bdf46bf87ebe6d7102f.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/91234/size6/6aa846d5dcfdb23cba7e5450061ced1f.jpg","text":"2/15","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/91223/size6/3e91f0cf7c9814f843145580bfdc192a.jpg","text":"Salut !\nJe m'appelle Anand.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90851/size6/a78d90d91032a700d7ec2675d5a79504.jpg","text":"Je ramasse les poubelles de ce quartier.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/91227/size6/e1c4e5a12553e9039a4fb680690b3255.jpg","text":"Quand je suis en retard, Madame Mascarenhas est en furie.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/91239/size6/6fc130502f85fa2124ee26975e9e5dbf.jpg","text":"Monsieur Unni tient à ce que je ramasse tous les déchets sans exception.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/91229/size6/8742fc3e0ba0f571e9a8197e2e9cd4c7.jpg","text":"Madame Anitha a l'odorat très délicat.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/91230/size6/515406c7130b1ec0099b25473a74822d.jpg","text":"Les nouveaux habitants au coin de la rue sont sympas,\ncontrairement à leur VILAIN chien !","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90856/size6/b28f6a293e3e40239c67e151ec781b0f.jpg","text":"Oh, non ! Ça va prendre une éternité à nettoyer, ça.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90857/size6/f3bc90929d9d9486b968e6a4d9aa35f8.jpg","text":"J'aime passer dans la rue où habite Salim.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90858/size6/ede2c4b652121cce43c49498bc125d24.jpg","text":"Salim et moi sommes très bons amis.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/91231/size6/2b2085196f9a78e2a10e6ab4aff707ca.jpg","text":"Il adore jouer du tambour et j'adore danser.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90860/size6/f0441a8f1ad00d9af684bee80d655a26.jpg","text":"Mais bientôt c'est l'heure d'y aller.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/91241/size6/50ffe308b9a99ed45877827cf9d6af4f.jpg","text":"Salut !","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/91233/size6/d361c5705b6f0ef3ca11db0abace7c57.jpg","text":"15/15","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":14,"words":101}}